VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT @\(\s*\(MarkupString\)\s*|new\s+MarkupString\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:HtmlEncoder|Sanitize|AntiXss|allowlist
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects MarkupString usage that renders raw HTML without sanitization.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for MarkupString Cast from User Input.
